     7â†’/// From motivation.md:
     8â†’/// > specORACLEã¯ã€ã€Œè¨¼æ˜ã•ã‚ŒãŸä¸–ç•Œã€ã‚’æä¾›ã™ã‚‹ã“ã¨ãŒæœ¬è³ªã§ã‚ã‚‹
     9â†’/// > "The essence of specORACLE is to provide a 'proven world'"
    10â†’///
    11â†’/// Current implementation: Z3 SMT solver (complete formal verification)
    12â†’/// Fallback: Lightweight constraint solver (when Z3 unavailable)
    13â†’
    14â†’mod z3_backend;
    15â†’
    16â†’use std::collections::HashMap;
